## POST-DEPLOYMENT: Monitoring

- [ ] **Uptime monitoring** — set up external monitor hitting `/health` endpoint
  (UptimeRobot free tier, or Cloudflare health check)
- [ ] **Error alerting** — configure PM2 or a log watcher to alert on repeated errors
- [ ] **Database monitoring** — DigitalOcean provides basic metrics; watch for:
  - Connection count approaching pool limit
  - Query latency spikes (the batch transaction adds ~1-2ms per query)
  - Disk usage growth
- [ ] **AI API spend monitoring** — check Cohere and Anthropic dashboards daily for
  the first week, then weekly

